  "title" : "Mod in Java produces negative numbers",
  "body" : "<p>When I calculate <code>int i = -1 % 2</code>  I get <code>-1</code> in Java. In Python, I  get <code>1</code> as the result of <code>-1 % 2</code>.\nWhat do I have to do to get the same behavior in Java with the modulo function?</p>\n"
